feed: Hey there! I'm Liyu, a high school student with a burning passion for website design, computer science, and all things mathematical. This website is my digital playground, where I showcase my projects, share my thoughts, and connect with fellow enthusiasts like you.

Current highschool student heavily interested in the aspects of website design and computer science. With a deep interest in mathematics and teaching, I have taught hundereds of students with over 750 hours of instruction ince then, I've spent countless hours tinkering with code, designing websites, and exploring the endless possibilities of computer science. Currently, im interested in game design and game development through java and python.
